<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-88-0011 </DOCNO><TEXT>Discusses air pollution regulation and methods of emission control appliedto coal handling and storage, and to smoke, particulates, sulphur oxidesand nitrogen oxides from coal. Other topics considered are trace elementemissions from coal, ash disposal, acid rain and carbon dioxide emissions.Two new technologies - the burning of coal liquid fuels and combinedcycle operation are briefly discussed. 21 refs., 2 tabs.</TEXT></DOC>